          {
            "title": "Local scope",
            "id": 86990,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Variables created inside a function have a <strong>local scope</strong>, like <code>bonus</code> here.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"add_bonus\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(salary)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" bonus = \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(salary + bonus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"add_bonus(\" /><text value=\"1900\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;bonus&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2000\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>bonus</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Local scope 2",
            "id": 86991,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>With a local scope, we can only access or update the variable within the function that created it. Try setting <code>bonus</code> to <code>200</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"add_bonus\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(salary)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" bonus = \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" bonus = \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(salary + bonus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"add_bonus(\" /><text value=\"1900\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"42\" /><option startIndex=\"43\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"48\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2100\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>bonus</code>, followed by <code>=</code>, and finally <code>200</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Error",
            "id": 86992,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>If we try to access or update the variable outside of the function block, like here with <code>bonus</code>, we'll get an error.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"add_bonus\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(salary)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" bonus = \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(salary + bonus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(bonus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"add_bonus(\" /><text value=\"1900\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"71\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"NameError: name 'bonus' is not defined\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>bonus</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
