          {
            "title": "Example: Local scope",
            "id": 87038,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Create the variable <code>discount</code>, that has a local scope inside the <code>apply_discount</code> function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"apply_discount\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(price)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  discount = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price - discount\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"final_price = apply_discount(\" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(final_price)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"37\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"30\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>discount</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Local scope 2",
            "id": 87039,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Update the variable <code>discount</code> to <code>10</code> within the local scope of <code>apply_discount</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"apply_discount\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(price)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  discount = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  discount = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price - discount\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"final_price = apply_discount(\" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(final_price)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"58\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"40\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>discount = 10</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Error",
            "id": 87040,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code a line to print the greeting message without accessing the variable <code>greeting</code> outside of its local scope of the <code>greet_user</code> function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"user = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Amy&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(name)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  greeting = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hi&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{greeting}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{user}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"!&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hi \" /><text value=\"{user}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"!&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"90\" /><option startIndex=\"90\" endIndex=\"91\" /><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"104\" /><option startIndex=\"104\" endIndex=\"105\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hi Amy!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>print</code> followed by <code>(</code> and then <code>f</code>, <code>\"Hi {user}!\"</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
