            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>When can we first access a variable, regardless of scope?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Only after we create it</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Before or after creating it</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Only after we create it.</p></body></html>"
